==强制陪同==
根据伊朗政府要求，{{flag|USA}}、{{flag|UK}}和{{flag|CAN}}公民在伊朗境内必须要有获得授权的伊朗向导全程陪同。<ref>http://www.iraniantours.com/us.htm {{Wayback|url=http://www.iraniantours.com/us.htm |date=20170903221959 }}  ESCORTED TOURS THROUGH IRAN</ref>

==拒绝入境==
伊朗政府拒绝任何{{flag|Israel}}公民、持有[[以色列护照|以色列护照]]者以及护照上有以色列签证或出入境章的外国人入境。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sitara.com/iran/visa.html |title=Travel in Iran |accessdate=2016-12-08 |archive-date=2012-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121127010907/http://sitara.com/iran/visa.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.timaticweb.com/cgi-bin/tim_website_client.cgi?SpecData=1&VISA=&page=visa&NA=IL&AR=00&PASSTYPES=PASS&DE=IR&user=KLMB2C&subuser=KLMB2C |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-12-08 |archive-date=2017-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215221532/https://www.timaticweb.com/cgi-bin/tim_website_client.cgi?SpecData=1&VISA=&page=visa&NA=IL&AR=00&PASSTYPES=PASS&DE=IR&user=KLMB2C&subuser=KLMB2C |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

同时对于女性入境，则有着装要求。如果女性在入境时未穿着长衫，长裤并围头巾或[[希贾布|希贾布]]等[[伊斯兰教|伊斯兰教]]服饰，也将被拒绝入境。<ref name=pw>{{cite web|title=Passport Information - Warning|url=https://www.timaticweb.com/cgi-bin/tim_website_client.cgi?FullText=1&COUNTRY=IR&SECTION=PA&SUBSECTION=WA&user=KLMB2C&subuser=KLMB2C|work=[[Timatic|Timatic]]|publisher=[[IATA|IATA]]|accessdate=17 December 2013|archive-date=2017-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215221530/https://www.timaticweb.com/cgi-bin/tim_website_client.cgi?FullText=1&COUNTRY=IR&SECTION=PA&SUBSECTION=WA&user=KLMB2C&subuser=KLMB2C|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

